There have been a couple circular robots throughout the years

There have been plenty of octagon bots as teams clip corners or have bumper lead-in angles to push through traffic at the peak of CIM usage and custom tank drive development.

There have been some tiny robots over the years, some competitive play, some off season.

Nonagon robots that make Einstein have a 100% conversation rate

2383 and 4907 had some strange ones this year, not sure what ultimately happened to 1942 this year (CINDERELLA 1942 FRC Robot Reveal, 2023 Season: The Road Runner)
